base_path <- here("code", "study1")
data_path <- paste0(base_path, "/snapshots_study1_preprocessing_analysis/data_processed_step1.csv")
d <- read_csv(data_path) %>% 
      mutate(
        subject_id = as.factor(subject_id),
        trial_type = as.factor(trial_type),
        trial_type_order = as.factor(trial_type_order),
        itemA = as.factor(itemA),
        itemB = as.factor(itemB),
        categoryA = as.factor(categoryA),
        categoryB = as.factor(categoryB)
      )

1.0.1 Metadata

1.0.1.1 Description

Dataset name: Step 1 Processed data showing raw x y coordinates of Sorted items, and raw Causal ratings

This dataset is generated by the pre-processing script and is a cleaned up version of the raw data. It contains x and y coordinates of the items in the sorting task, response values for the causal task, and a few extra columns
